#: .\core\presets.py:5
msgid "1-4-2 Lung Conditioning Pattern"
msgstr "1-4-2 肺部调理模式"

#: .\core\presets.py:13
msgid ""
"A classic respiratory conditioning sequence designed to maximize blood "
"oxygenation and expand vital lung capacity over time."
msgstr "经典的呼吸调节序列，旨在最大化血液含氧量并随着时间的推移扩大肺活量。"

#: .\core\presets.py:16
msgid "Box Breathing (Navy SEAL Tactical Clarity)"
msgstr "箱式呼吸（海豹突击队战术清明法）"

#: .\core\presets.py:24
msgid ""
"The gold standard for high-stress grounding. Equal duration phases clear "
"cortisol, settle racing hearts, and restore sharp mental clarity."
msgstr ""
"高压下恢复镇定的黄金标准。等长的各个阶段有助于清除皮质醇、平复心跳并恢复敏锐"
"的精神状态。"

#: .\core\presets.py:27
msgid "4-7-8 Relaxation (Nervous System Tranquilizer)"
msgstr "4-7-8 放松法（神经系统镇静剂）"

#: .\core\presets.py:35
msgid ""
"Acts as a natural chemical brake for your sympathetic nervous system. Highly "
"recommended for severe anxiety and floating into deep sleep."
msgstr "作为交感神经系统的天然化学制动器。强烈推荐用于缓解严重焦虑和助眠。"

#: .\core\presets.py:38
msgid "Coherent / Resonant Breathing (Asthma & Panic Relief)"
msgstr "谐振呼吸（哮喘与恐慌缓解）"

#: .\core\presets.py:46
msgid ""
"Balances the vagus nerve and optimizes heart rate variability (HRV). Zero "
"hold times make this perfectly safe for active asthma management."
msgstr ""
"平衡迷走神经并优化心率变异性 (HRV)。无需屏气，因此对活动性哮喘管理绝对安全。"

#: .\core\presets.py:49
msgid "Tactical Breathing (Sustained Equilibrium)"
msgstr "战术呼吸（持续平衡）"

#: .\core\presets.py:57
msgid ""
"A specialized, low-overhead holding variant used by responders to reduce "
"somatic anxiety without inducing lightheadedness."
msgstr "一种由救援人员使用的低负荷屏气变体，用于减轻躯体焦虑而不引起头晕。"

#: .\core\presets.py:60
msgid "Pursed-Lip Splinting (COPD & Air-Trapping Relief)"
msgstr "缩唇呼吸（COPD与气体滞留缓解）"

#: .\core\presets.py:68
msgid ""
"Creates passive mechanical backpressure to keep bronchial pathways open. "
"Crucial for individuals with emphysema or structural shortness of breath."
msgstr ""
"产生被动机械反压以保持支气管通路开放。对肺气肿或结构性呼吸急促患者至关重要。"

#: .\core\presets.py:71
msgid "Physiological Sigh (Acute Hyperventilation Intercept)"
msgstr "生理性叹息（急性过度通气阻截）"

#: .\core\presets.py:79
msgid ""
"Simulates the biological double-inhale reflex to instantly re-inflate "
"collapsed alveoli and maximize immediate carbon dioxide unloading."
msgstr ""
"模拟生物体的双重吸气反射，瞬间使萎陷的肺胞重新充气，并最大化即时的二氧化碳排"
"出。"

#: .\core\presets.py:82
msgid "Extended Cardiac Exhale (Hypertension / Vagal Tone)"
msgstr "延长呼气法（高血压/迷走神经张力控制）"

#: .\core\presets.py:90
msgid ""
"Exhale window is mathematically doubled relative to inhale. Maximizes "
"acetylcholinergic outflow to safely downregulate heart rate and blood "
"pressure."
msgstr ""
"呼气时间在数学上是吸气时间的两倍。最大化乙酰胆碱输出，以安全地降低心率和血"
"压。"

